sentenceData.sentence: those who used Adderall® nonmedically in the past year were more than 1.5 times as likely as their counterparts to have used alcohol in the past month (95.4 vs. 63.0 percent),
more than twice as likely to have been binge alcohol users (89.5 vs. 41.4 percent),
and more than 3 times as likely to have been heavy alcohol users (55.2 vs. 15.6 percent)
